{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_06_02",
  "title": "川咲さくら 2話 あの人を超えないと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ラジオをお聞きのみなさん、こんにちは～！\nサニーピースの川咲さくらです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ everyone listening to the radio!\nIt's Sakura Kawasaki from Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.7736507415
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "先日開催が発表された、NEXT VENUS\nグランプリ歴代優勝者による夢の祭典！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today‚ I'll be bringing you the latest information about\nthe upcoming NEXT VENUS Grand Prix‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.1333333015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "この番組では、気になる祭典の情報を\nどこよりも早くお届けしちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "a dream festival featuring past champions!\nWe'll be delivering information about this event faster than",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.3333338101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8852397919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "生放送中にみなさんのメッセージも紹介するので\nじゃんじゃん送って下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "anywhere else on this show‚ so\nplease send in your messages during this live broadcast!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8333347003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日のさくらの仕事は、祭典の情報を紹介する）\n（生放送特番のメインパーソナリティだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura's job today is to introduce information about the festival.）\n（She's the main host of this live special.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.7737657865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8070958138
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "――という訳で、イベントに参加する\n歴代優勝者のみなさんを紹介させていただきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So‚ I've introduced all the past champions who will be participating in the event.\nI can't believe I get to perform with such amazing people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7113203049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.1265970231
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに凄い人達と共演出来るなんて\n夢みたいでドキドキしてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This feels like a dream come true‚ and I'm so excited.\nSunny Peace will be singing Mana-san's song together with",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2999980609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9098843575
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "今回サニピは月ストと一緒に麻奈さんの曲を歌います\nサニピと月ストの共演、私もすっごく楽しみです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest this time. I'm really looking forward to the collaboration\nbetween Sunny Peace and Moon Tempest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5999975522,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ここまで、落ち着いて進行出来ているな）\n（この調子なら安心して見ていられそうだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She's been managing this calmly until now.）\n（At this rate‚ I can relax and watch.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4969392141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.7636053722
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "リスナーさんからメッセージが届いてるので\nいくつか紹介しますね。質問にも答えちゃいますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have messages from our listeners‚\nso let me introduce a few. I'll also answer your questions!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5333326657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.1158276241
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "最初のメッセージは、「麻奈さんの曲をカバーするって\n決まった時の心境を教えて下さい」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The first message is‚ \"Please tell us how you felt when\nyou found out you'd be covering Mana-san's song for the event.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2999993324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね……麻奈さんは尊敬する先輩なので\n嬉しいのと同じくらい責任重大だなって思いました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… Mana-san is a senior I deeply respect‚\nso I felt a great sense of responsibility as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8666659991,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.7293860118
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "次のメッセージは、「サニピは麻奈さんを超えたと\n言われてますが……」って、そんなことありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The next message is‚ \"Sunny Peace is said to\nhave surpassed Mana-san…\" but that's not true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5666639645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.3333306312
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "私なんてまだまだです、麻奈さんには全然敵いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm far from it. I can't rival Mana-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.6155090015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9607694309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（急に慌て始めたな。もしかしてこの間麻奈を超えたと）\n（言われた時から、ずっと気にしていたのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She suddenly seems flustered.）\n（Did she start worrying about this since the announcement?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3941027642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.660767905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "「I-UNITY決勝のサニピのライブは\nとても素晴らしくて感動しました」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I was deeply moved by Sunny Peace's performance\nat the I-UNITY finals‚\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.06666193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "「麻奈さんの伝説の星見まつりのライブを\n超えていたと思います」……そんなことないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I believe they've surpassed Mana-san's legendary\nHoshimi Festival performance.\" But that's not true…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5333285967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.7826494854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "「麻奈さんの曲をサニピが歌うことは、新旧アイドルの\n世代交代を象徴する出来事に……」って、待って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Sunny Peace singing Mana-san's song is an event symbolizing\nthe generational shift in idols…\" Wait a minute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3666609127,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.0822732609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "ですから、世代交代とか、麻奈さん超えとか\nそんなこと期待されても……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So even if they expect a generational shift\nor surpassing Mana-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.4000034014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さくら……顔色が真っ青だが、大丈夫なのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura… She looks pale‚ is she okay?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.867239539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_radio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "radio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.1005647343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、ごめんなさい\nなんだか変な空気になっちゃいましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ I'm sorry.\nIt seems like the atmosphere got a bit strange.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0333285967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "気を取り直して、ここからは\nイベントの最新情報をお届けします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's get back on track and\nbring you the latest information about the event!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2333285967,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（さくらは笑顔で番組を進行しているが）\n（ぎこちなさは隠し切れていないな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sakura is hosting the show with a smile‚ but…）\n（She can't completely hide her unease.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.4420681954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その夜",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That night",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.1754015287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-night",
      "startTime": 171.2753933908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "1、2、3、4……1、2、3、4……",
      "translations": {
