      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが、無理は禁物だ\n寮まで送るから今日は帰って休むんだ。いいな",
